Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:44.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been playing the same fighting games lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If I don't have my glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.32,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}BON-BON Cheerleaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.89,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get! Cherry pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.48,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}RAN-RAN Welcome party
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.09,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look up! Sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:51.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.16,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The presence... of asteroids!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:55.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As they confoundedly collide and melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.54,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sing loudly! Like a Sirenger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.70,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:03.15,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be the one with the last laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:10.05,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I'm wearing a sailor uniform {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}And that's that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.31,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it's only Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.80,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm feeling horrible. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:22.85,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The summer clothes are so much better! {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}Oh, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.96,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's getting close to 3 picts. Yet, I'm still hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:30.00,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try your best! Get your spirits up! My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:02.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:03.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:05.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:32.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:34.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We switch to summer uniforms today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:37.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like Konata will probably show up in her winter uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:40.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At least one person in our class will forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:42.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's one in this house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:58.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to sign up for the TV drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:01:59.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:00.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda wanted the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:02.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An apron from Apron of Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:07.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot because you don't have enough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:08.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:12.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More like I've been busy with student council stuff and tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:13.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:14.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are just excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:17.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:20.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me on the same level as\Nsomeone who only ever thinks about having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the way you put it really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you win a drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:26.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a loveless woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:33.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you jot down the usual stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're not going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you put on yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:39.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff that'll help me win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good handwriting is a fundamental must.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:47.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to design a postcard that just begs to be drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:48.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:50.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:53.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Use a fluorescent marker to draw a border around the postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:03:00.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you add a picture related to the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:04.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't draw very well though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...just send in as many entries as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can probably handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many you send...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:19.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...write each one out without using a printer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And send out a hundred each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:22.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that cost a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fighting for something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:31.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That calls for passion and guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't it be cheaper just to buy it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some things in this world can't be bought with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fit a hundred postcards in a mailbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't send them all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but a few here and a few there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And over the course of a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on who's running the drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:53.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you might get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:57.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sometimes you're better off without the tricky stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes it's the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:01.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:01.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:02.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if you want to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...glance through free newspapers and flyers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:12.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and look for drawings that\Nprobably aren't going to attract many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have a high chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:15.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where's the love in that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, for twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you don't look anything like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 'cause we're fraternal twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Identical twins look exactly the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:31.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's more like comparing sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but fraternal twins can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...pretty different in appearance and personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa is laid-back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:41.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Kagami is pretty crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:42.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:45.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had the same hairstyles with the same ribbons...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you might end up looking the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kona-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami could never be the cutesy type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:52.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:55.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult me with your weird fantasies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you use telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:58.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when they're raised separately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:06.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...they end up having similar lifestyles and significant others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes they end up marrying another pair of twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:11.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when one of them is in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:14.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the other one can sense it from a completely different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:17.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are all kinds of mysterious phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So can't you use telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:21.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Abracadabra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You read way too much manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Same with ManaKana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,ManaKana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that they have a few differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Mana is the careful one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Kana is the optimistic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:37.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And apparently they sound a little different when they sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:42.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,ManaKana thought they were fraternal twins for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:45.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they recently learned that\Nthey were actually identical twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:51.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The definitions for identical and fraternal twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...have changed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that you two could be identical twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your identical traits would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You both like sweets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:03.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:04.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:09.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite color?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,White maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:11.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The same colors as your souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:22.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All this talk about eggs and black\Nand white cookies has made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was talking about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's suffocating in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got on and I've already broken a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't turned on the air conditioning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:53.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladybug Samba, punk version.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my cousins is getting married this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So she'll be a June bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:03.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How does this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:10.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wet and gloomy season supposedly signify happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:16.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does getting married in June make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The name June...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is generally said to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:23.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...derived from the name of the Roman goddess, Juno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:24.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In Greek mythology...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:27.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Juno is known as Hera...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the goddess of marriage and fertility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:33.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why those who get married\Nin Hera's month, the month of June...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:36.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...are said to receive her protection and blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:40.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't Hera Zeus's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this image of Hera being extremely jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'm not feeling this happy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:48.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:52.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather wear a dress or a kimono for your wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I would wear a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been my dream since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd also go with a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But a kimono would also be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna wear both!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:10.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They have miniskirts and really colorful dresses these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A miniskirt wedding dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:16.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd look really cute with lots of frills on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of frills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:20.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:22.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Angel Salvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:22.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:25.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair makes you look more like Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So a yellow top and miniskirt it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd probably look good in a miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:33.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dress is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the person you're getting married to is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or a rich lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough choice to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One has lots of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:48.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the ability to cast Beho*mi and l***zun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But as far as feelings are concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bianca hands down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the true love type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd go for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No comeback, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a question about a game I borrowed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:09.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, Kagaminya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it more fun when you figure it out yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:18.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you understand that you should do things yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll do your own homework from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the detectives in manga and TV shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:28.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...run into an awful lot of murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like in Conan or Kindaichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:33.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There wouldn't be a story otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't they just solve normal cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:41.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like travel around Japan in search of missing persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tailing people would translate well into a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With plenty of thrill and suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:51.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could also conduct investigations into unfaithful wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:53.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or look for pets that ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But would that be fun to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:00.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cases in real life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:05.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't really use any brilliant tricks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...like the ones you find in manga and TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:14.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabricated fingerprints that can't be\Ndetected through a luminol reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff that's a step ahead of forensic labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:17.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything too good might lead to copycats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or be too sensitive for broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, or that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:28.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The really hard cases end without\Nanyone realizing they happened or go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:28.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:31.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be wrong in so many ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hate how it's been\Nconstantly raining the past few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I used to like rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You get soaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you can't hang clothes out to dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I've never really liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you like rain, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:55.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because baseball games would be\Ncancelled and I'd get to watch anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds just like something you would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:00.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a lot more dome stadiums now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:06.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:13.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You often see idiots and geniuses\Ngoing to the same school in anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease that immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, neener-neener!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that actually kinda strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...in some recent anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:27.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the teacher looks the same age as the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ta*****na-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:35.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's always been interested in watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the gap between physical age and mental age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:42.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't question it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:45.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, wouldn't a student who's\Nreally different from everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...be the real mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:52.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree one hundred percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be saying this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't know how you got into this school, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at putting stuff off till the night before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you didn't study until the night before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:06.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mean she really did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:08.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't have pulled it off in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That gave me a scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:15.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm impressed that you actually kept studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:18.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a quiz game come out for DS or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:20.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad set some conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A D-rank would mean a Pippin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A C-rank would mean a 3DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A B-rank would mean a PS2.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Papa Izumi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You really know how to deal with your daughter, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:39.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the real mystery how Tsukasa's in the same school as us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:46.01,ls_alternative_2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come back in ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:41.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it without even blinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:45.97,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:47.70,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I can't beat her at fighting games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:46.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}I won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.13,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}She's spent way more time on them than I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:52.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Challenge to me a different game if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:54.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A quiz game!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:02.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to Konata in a game of knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she memorized the question order?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.07,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:10.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\i1}Her memory's incredible when it comes to gaming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we play next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have a really easy party game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know all the games I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could probably beat me at that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It just stunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've barely eaten any snacks, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, you wolf them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no real reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieting for summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:43.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like you have anyone to show your swimsuit off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:43.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:45.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:47.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you guys born on Tanabata?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your birthday soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered our birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen's right before the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In the year before a critical year...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...unlucky things begin to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As our birthday approaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm getting worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:11.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I bought a bunch of wards...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and power stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop buying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:18.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have wards against rage at our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All-purpose ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wards against rage, hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:25.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:29.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We ensure safe pregnancy and protect\Nyou from traffic accidents at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:30.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:35.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that your birthday is Ponytail Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why July 7th?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:43.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Vega from the Tanabata legend had a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:49.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Japan Ponytail Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:54.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they give an award every year to a\Ncelebrity who they think would look good with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:15:00.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a feeling that anyone would look good with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My hair's the shortest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:10.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so it's barely a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:14.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But a little ponytail's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours also looks good, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could go with that on an everyday basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:19.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:21.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami's is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:30.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:31.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll undo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All manly like a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:41.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drunks often wear ties around their heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to mean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just when the guy loosens the tie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and tries to pull it off over his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it gets stuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:53.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:56.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's a lot weirder that they're always carrying a takeout box.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeout box?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing Kato-chan from the Drifters carries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drunks these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:09.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...pretty much always have a tie around\Ntheir head and a takeout box in their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:14.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Vega and Altair meet this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine. Shine. Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope those rage wards of yours can deliver a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're giving away all varieties of QUO cards at Comp Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:25.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always collecting QUO cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but do you ever use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why spend the effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it natural to want any item...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...related to a series you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As a fan. As a collector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you're never gonna use them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take good care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:49.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really pisses me off when I see someone use one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to use these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:55.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Much less auction them off or sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Using them makes you a surefire failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a fan and as a collector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't say anything when you're so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:05.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, I need at least three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One for preservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep it in a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:13.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then one to take out occasionally to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the last one for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:14.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:15.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:21.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you always want two or three of something you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:24.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:27.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd expect Tsukasa to be popular with guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I've never heard anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:40.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's a little plain and doesn't really stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because she's got a scary sister guarding her like a hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I'm really plain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:50.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or if it's more that Kona-chan and Yuki-chan are really unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki knows all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Has a good figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wears glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hates the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.40,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.03,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Isn't this getting a little weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true that I haven't heard anything about Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because she's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that everyone's afraid to approach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:09.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and really good at helping others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a lot of guys ask her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she turns them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Turns them down, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:18.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:21.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she doesn't realize that they're asking her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan can be a little clueless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:27.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so an indirect approach might not work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:30.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the guys in your class are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't a single one of them have the guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to confess his passionate feelings to Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:37.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:40.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough maniacs in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:43.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san's type is usually a bigger hit with maniacs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniacs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:48.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:49.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:54.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:58.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue to enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:01.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Buh-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:07.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Going on with the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that person was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:14.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that always happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody does it at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:28.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was definitely an element of moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:33.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:34.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:46.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's another whoo-whoo happy episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:49.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:53.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:54.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us have now done this show...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:19:59.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Three times after today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about it, Shiraishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:10.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like Shiraishi-san hasn't opened up to me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like we're sitting further apart than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they mean by emotional distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:16.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:20.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get rollin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got something the fans will love today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be doing our first\Nintroduction for a member of the regular cast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Da! Da-da-dum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be introducing Miyuki Takara-san today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:37.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:41.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The class representative, well-mannered, kn—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowledgeable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:46.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...in both literary and culinary arts. A perfect person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:49.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Miyuki-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so wonderful, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First, there's her glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she's pretty as a button.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With those looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'd expect her to be hard to approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:03.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she's actually a friendly person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:06.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd talk that much on the radio show...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:09.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop talking when it's about Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:12.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:13.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki Takara-san, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:17.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With large breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And other various elements of moe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:22.08,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama, that's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:22.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she so lucky to be a pretty character?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The maniacs love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:24.65,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(54,691)}Uh, maniacs is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:24.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's maniacs you want, I'm a huge hit with those lolicons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:29.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:39.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Send us any questions or comments about the show, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:45.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's she really like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she like smoke a pack at a time backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:53.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No worry of that. She isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A unique song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:03.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear a song that normal people can enjoy already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the next one, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:08.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it from the intro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:10.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not another weird song, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:15.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was this song again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:16.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:17.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:18.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:21.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from FMP. FMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:24.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's Kagami's favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:25.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumoffu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:26.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:28.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just read the novels...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:29.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and got a little hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:35.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:37.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can also sound like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:39.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she just doing an imitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:43.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:45.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two going to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:48.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's anything I can sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:50.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know very many songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:51.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything works.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:55.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sing what you want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:56.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:58.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:00.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very confident about my singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:01.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:03.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones who'll hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:04.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:06.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:07.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:28.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:28.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:29.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I laughed so hard the other day that I couldn't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:34.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at school one morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:36.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already out of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:36.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:37.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Motivation Issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to next time!
