Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:39.75,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Say a day were to come when tears begin to fall...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.24,0:22:47.09,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}...I would want your back for comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:58.73,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Kindness can be very cruel at times...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.43,0:23:08.45,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The more we try, the more we lose sight of the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:16.82,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}If you can see rainbows in our town after the rain has just passed...
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.65,0:23:20.83,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Then let's set out now.
